moji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4ccc654f166fdb14b66987948f6aba2b96d509f","tid":801891,"uid":1158,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"53afdb46cc1912a5ab5af2897082992994dfac03","tid":801891,"uid":48917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T04:34:38.000Z","msg":"大家好<br />\n小弟家中牆已出現大量霉菌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n過左幾年終於頂唔順 要自己出手搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因出面搵裝修太貴了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想自己油<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n想問問各位巴絲<br />\n小弟住公屋<br />\n唔個太熟牆 的特質<br />\n現時四牆都有霉菌<br />\n天花板開始有<br />\n我自己買工具 自己搞<br />\n需要剷灰先嗎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇話用咩油漆？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇新手教學？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上網睇 都唔太明<br />\nThx"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T09:09:43.000Z","msg":"如果自己做,唔需要剷灰<br />\n灰係指油漆下面果層,你剷灰就要重新批灰,如果你本身冇經驗,真係好難做,因為好大機會整到個牆身一舊舊,好難睇,所以千祈唔好剷<br />\n<br />\n重新油要買以下用品:<br />\n1. 100紅沙*5-10張<br />\n2 雞毛掃<br />\n3.立邦多功能油掃<br />\n4.立邦5合1油漆2罐 (睇你想用咩色,白色就好易污糟,建議你買1902米黃色)<br />\n5.水施那一支<br />\n<br />\n先用雞毛掃掃清牆身所有垃圾,再用紅沙係起霉地方博命係咁刷刷刷,其實起霉地方係冇可能100%刷得甩,總之盡力而為啦,,,之後就可以用水稀釋水施那,油晒所有牆身,等佢乾透,就可以稀釋油漆,上色,上色唔可能一次搞掂,最少都要油3,4次,就係咁簡單"},{"pid":"58b54026cb816d0fa18063bba6e38017adc4049b","tid":801891,"uid":48917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f4ccc654f166fdb14b66987948f6aba2b96d509f","tid":801891,"uid":1158,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"53afdb46cc1912a5ab5af2897082992994dfac03","tid":801891,"uid":48917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTim