<br />\n一噴完就會無晒<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.kao.com/hk/kao_imgs/magiclean/mcl_bath_toile_00_img_l.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.kao.com%2Fhk%2Fkao_imgs%2Fmagiclean%2Fmcl_bath_toile_00_img_l.jpg&h=0f4ab7ed&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T06:35:00.000Z","msg":"牆岩用？<br />\n以前有一支用黎噴水龍頭關節位<br />\n都有用<br />\n但依家自己屋企想變返以前岩岩搬入去果時咁白雪雪"},{"pid":"302e4308951c744bf07cc32c4a9e9c27d477bf89","tid":801891,"uid":117008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T06:43:22.000Z","msg":"真心 唔識就唔好搞 <br />\n利申同老豆8月全屋批灰上灰油油 唔係做裝修但係大家都識點搞 叫有經驗 問題係到依家都仲整緊 已經問人借曬機去做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1803dae97d0eac73a2cc1723588ba713b5bc0468","tid":801891,"uid":119409,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T07:02:42.000Z","msg":"唔識唔好搞.唔係買油返黎油咁簡單<br />\n早幾年我都係咁諗.<br />\n自己買左D油返黎油.<br />\n油完係好好呀<br />\n唔夠3日一塊塊紙咁甩返出黎<br />\n先自己上網睇.牆太奈歷史上油跟本唔會上得實<br />\n要成個牆刪晒D灰.再重新上灰.再磨平上油<br />\n好大工程.簡單D方法就係用&quot;水C嗱&quot;將舊牆嗱實<br />\n再上油.我就係咁做.但唔夠一年又開始甩油<br />\n所以你唔識自己搞.分分鐘衰過唔搞"},{"pid":"f7cb8eb9354bf16d51441a7231d9448feb7aae96","tid":801891,"uid":78666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5c2ccee215c93ebebafd25a9b5916f2f653a4dbe","tid":801891,"uid":48917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1cc1fddaf44e5abd54611c8d3a406ee1c61c340d","tid":801891,"uid":78666,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T04:05:08.000Z","msg":"如果純粹想除霉<br />\n可以買枝 萬潔靈<br />\n一噴完就會無晒<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.kao.com/hk/kao_imgs/magiclean/mcl_bath_toile_00_img_l.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.kao.com%2Fhk%2Fkao_imgs%2Fmagiclean%2Fmcl_bath_toile_00_img_l.jpg&h=0f4ab7ed&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T06:35:00.000Z","msg":"牆岩用？<br />\n以前有一支用黎噴水龍頭關節位<br />\n都有用<br />\n但依家自己屋企想變返以前岩岩搬入去果時咁白雪雪"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T08:11:36.000Z","msg":"我自己試過係得<br 